President Obama has nominated Judge J. Michelle Childs and Richard Mark Gergel to the District Court bench for the District of South Carolina. Judge Childs currently serves on the South Carolina Circuit Court and has experience in various legal roles, including Acting Justice for the South Carolina Supreme Court. Richard Mark Gergel is a principal and senior partner at a law firm in South Carolina, specializing in personal injury litigation and employment discrimination matters. Both nominees have demonstrated integrity and a commitment to justice throughout their careers.